### StateMachine

#### lifecycle

##### State

###### Draft

####### Transition
- to :: Review
- on :: submit
- guard :: paymentConfirmed
- action :: submitForReview

####### Transition
- to :: Published
- on :: publish
- guard :: event.amount > 0 && reviewerApproved
- action :: publishDirect

###### Review

####### Transition
- to :: Published
- on :: approve
- guard :: event.score >= 80
- action :: publishFromReview

####### Transition
- to :: Draft
- on :: reject
- guard :: reviewerRejected || event.reasonPresent
- action :: backToDraft

